Alaafin of Oyo, Oba Lamidi Adeyemi, has picked a wife, who bears the same name with the lover of popular singer, Davido. In one of their rare outings together, Chioma, the new wife, was seen with the monarch at a social function. This is the first time that the monarch, who has numerous wives, will tie the knots with someone from the Eastern part of the country. Below is the picture of the new queen:  Photo credit: City People